This page aims to surface a multi-dimensional view of product by collecting the various facets that contribute to category health for ongoing review and improvement. Visit [maturity](/direction/maturity/) to see our framework for categories, application types, and stages that considers adoption and user experience.

**X** indicates a a field that is not applicable. A blank field indicates applicatble, but missing or unavailable data. 

_Note: [How this data is aggregated, and instructions on what fields required updated are below.](#how-this-works)_

