## How this works

This data is gathered primarily from the `categories.yml` and `stages.yml` files. This table shows where each field comes from, indicating what needs to be added and where:

| Field                     | File                                                                                                  | Property                                          | Notes                                                                                 |
|---------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Group                     | [`stages.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/stages.yml)            | `name`                                            |                                                                                       |
| Category                  | [`categories.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/categories.yml)    | `name`                                            |                                                                                       |
| Direction                 | [`categories.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/categories.yml)    | `direction`                                       |                                                                                       |
| Investment Plan           | _none_                                                                                                | _n/a_                                             | _Links to `/handbook/product/investment`, with anchor based on group name_           |
| GMAU                      | [`stages.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/stages.yml)            | `pi_gmau`                                         | _Expected to be a link_                                                               |
| Paid GMAU                 | [`stages.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/stages.yml)            | `pi_pgmau`                                        | _Expected to be a link_                                                               |
| Analyst Reports           | [`stages.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/stages.yml)            | `analyst_reports`                                 | _Expected to be a list of `title` and `url`_                                                               |
| Competitive Comparison    | [`stages.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/stages.yml)            | `comp_comparison`                                 | _Expected to be a link_                                                               |
| Current Maturity          | [`categories.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/categories.yml)    | `maturity`                                        |                                                                                       |
| Planned Maturity          | [`categories.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/categories.yml)    | `available` / `viable` / `complete` / `lovable`   |                                                                                       |
| UX Scorecard              | [`categories.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/categories.yml)    | `ux_scorecard_link` & `ux_scorecard_score`        | _Link should be a link, Score should be a letter grade_                               |
| Usability Issues          | [`categories.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/categories.yml)    | `label`                                           | _Links to issue search based on label_                                                |
| Dogfooding?               | [`categories.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/categories.yml)    | `dogfooding_issue` & `dogfooding_status`          | _Issue should be a link, Status should be a text value_                               |
| Works by default?         | _none_                                                                                                | _n/a_                                             | _Links to `/handbook/product/works-by-default`, with anchor based on group name_      |
| Auto DevOps               | _unimplemented_                                                                                       |                                                   | _Not currently implemented, nothing to link to curently_                              |
| Capacity                  | [`stages.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/stages.yml)            | `be_team_tag` / `fe_team_tag` / `fs_team_tag`     |                                                                                       |
| Velocity                  | _unimplemented_                                                                                       |                                                   | _Not currently implemented._                                                          |
| Top Issues                | [`categories.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/categories.yml)    |                                                   | _Links to issue search based on label_                                                |
| Docs                      | [`categories.yml`](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/blob/master/data/categories.yml)    | `documentation`                                   |                                                                                       |
